title: [Emerald Forest, Fern Tunnel]
description: Tree ferns on tall, slender trunks stand sentinel here, aloft in a viridian sea of waving fronds.  Dappled light falls through the lacy screen and dances playfully across the shifting surfaces.  The shadowy alcoves harbor cooler air in their mysterious depths.
